Win yeṭṭsen ar azal, ad d-yettazzal.
Ad tt-id-ẓẓgen ur turiw.
Aql-i am seksu ddaw texsayt.
Am ma yennɣel yiẓi ɣef tasa.
Ulac win ara ixedmen deg tament ur tt-yemciḥ ara.
Rrwa akka i yettarwat, yelli-k wi bɣun yaɣ-itt.
Ur ttaɣ aɣyul deg tefsut, ur xeṭṭeb deg tmeɣra.
A yemma! Cebbḥeɣ ur ddiɣ. A yelli! Ur d-nnin ara ugiɣ.
Aṣurdi ur teḥbis texriḍt, ur ḥesseb d ṛṛas lmal.
Yiwen wass, i tkeḥḥel tyaziḍt yečča-tt wuccen.
Lḥila n ssbaṛ teččur, 
Wellah ar d taculliḍt n ṛṛay!
Tinna! d taculliḍt n teḍsa.
D temẓi i ixeddmen ɣef temɣer.
Akken tɣelli zzarriɛa i tmeɣɣi.
Yuɣal uqelmun s iḍarren.
A bu snat, bru i yiwet.
A win iɣef yeshel walluy, ḥader iman-ik deg trusi.
A win ijebbden amrar, ixef-is ha-t-a da ɣur-i.
Yufa uzduz afus-is.
Win i ten-yesɛan deg udrar, ur yettaggad aẓaɣar.
Seg ucrured ɣar tikli.
S ufella yecbaḥ yerqem, daxel mi d-teldiḍ yerka.
Yexdem umɣar ayen yexdem uqrur armi d tameddit, yemmut.
Ddiɣ d yir arfiq, yeǧǧa-yi deg yir amḍiq.
Amɣar mi icab ɣas neɣ-it.
Am win iceṭḥen i uderɣal.
Win i ak-ibeddlen s yibiw, kečč beddel-it s yiclem-is.
Yiwen wass i tettɛeddi ɣef wuccen.
Tfuh a taga, wwan ibawen.
